title: Graebel Van Lines Named Official Mover of the Dallas Cowboys
text:
Graebel Van Lines
DALLAS, Oct. 6, Graebel Van Lines, the Dallas-headquartered company, announced today that it has been named the "Official Mover of the Dallas Cowboys." Graebel Van Lines will be participating in a wide range of marketing and promotional opportunities from stadium signage to Dallascowboys.com and more.
Graebel Van Lines is the nation's largest, wholly-owned leading national mobility network known for corporate and consumer moving. The 65-year-old company also offers a comprehensive list of workspace solutions.
"Graebel Van Lines is thrilled to be the Official Mover and associated with the Dallas Cowboys," said Graebel Van Lines Owner and Chairman Vauna Peterson . Graebel Van Lines joins other recognizable brands that have partnered with the Dallas Cowboys over the club's tenure.
"The Dallas Cowboys are thrilled to partner with Graebel Van Lines," said Eric Sudol , Dallas Cowboys Vice President, Corporate Partnership Sales and Service. "This is an outstanding opportunity for us to team up with a locally-headquartered, nationally-known brand that has been a recognized leader in the moving industry across the country for 65 years."
Jack Donnell , Graebel Van Lines' Chief Commercial Officer said: "At Graebel Van Lines, we recognize that our customers and the nation's sports fans appreciate corporate relationships with major sports brands. A partnership with the Dallas Cowboys allows Graebel Van Lines the best platform to show customers our goal of providing them with a great move."
ABOUT GRAEBEL VAN LINES
Graebel Van Lines is a leader in moving and workspace solutions, serving the corporate, residential, workspace and international market segments. For 65 years, the company has built its reputation by offering the highest quality end-to-end customer experience for moves across the United States and internationally. The company also provides expertise in workspace moves, customized storage, installation, warehousing and inventory services for all types of businesses. Graebel Van Lines is committed to exceptional customer service and great moves for its consumer, corporate and workspace clients provided through best practices, processes and technology by experienced employees across the country.
To view the original version on PR Newswire, visit: http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/graebel-van-lines-named-official-mover-of-the-dallas-cowboys-300154994.html
